para cada classe existe:
hp increase: 0% a 25%
armor per grit: 1.0 a 10
base crit: 0% a 25%
crit chance scale: strenght / agility / vitality / authority / grit / expertise / sorcery / max health
crit scale rate: 0% a 25%

base crit damage: 0% a 25%
crit damage scale: strenght / agility / vitality / authority / grit / expertise / sorcery / max health
crit scale rate: 0% a 25%

primary: strenght / agility / vitality / authority / grit / expertise / sorcery / max health
secondary: strenght / agility / vitality / authority / grit / expertise / sorcery / max health
minor: strenght / agility / vitality / authority / grit / expertise / sorcery / max health
